"nibbattitvā uppatitvā paritte tiṇapuñje vā kaṭṭhapuñje vā nipateyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:6.5"
msgid ""
"Sā tattha aggimpi janeyya, dhūmampi janeyya, aggimpi janetvā dhūmampi "
"janetvā tameva parittaṃ tiṇapuñjaṃ vā kaṭṭhapuñjaṃ vā pariyādiyitvā anāhārā "
"nibbāyeyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:6.6"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ paṭipanno hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:6.7"
msgid "‘no cassa no ca me siyā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:6.8"
msgid ""
"so pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī "
"hoti. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
