"nibbattitvā uppatitvā vipule tiṇapuñje vā kaṭṭhapuñje vā nipateyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:7.5"
msgid ""
"Sā tattha aggimpi janeyya, dhūmampi janeyya, aggimpi janetvā dhūmampi "
"janetvā tameva vipulaṃ tiṇapuñjaṃ vā kaṭṭhapuñjaṃ vā pariyādiyitvā anāhārā "
"nibbāyeyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:7.6"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ paṭipanno hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.55:7.7"
